        "ProposedThresholdParameters": {
          "description": "A proposed set of threshold parameters submitted to `vote_new_parameters`: the proposed [`ThresholdParameters`] plus per-domain `ReconstructionThreshold` updates for the resharing it would trigger. An empty `per_domain_thresholds` keeps the current ones; a populated map must reference only existing domains (contract-validated), is applied to the `DomainRegistry` on resharing, and never persists onto the stored [`ThresholdParameters`].",
          "type": "object",
